      "stem_html": "Allene, H<sub>2</sub>C<span data-math=\"\\text{=}\"></span>C<span data-math=\"\\text{=}\"></span>CH<sub>2</sub>, has a heat of hydrogenation of –298 kJ/mol (–71.3 kcal/mol). Rank a conjugated diene, a nonconjugated diene, and an allene in order of stability.",
